# Student Report Filter
A file students.txt contains records in format:
Name,Marks,City
Extract and save only students scoring above 75 into a new file

#Algorithm :- Open student.txt in read mode
              Open new file (say output.txt) in write mode
              Read file line by line
              Split each line using comma ,
              Extract marks------>If marks ≥ 75 → write that line into new file Repeat till end Close files
#Code
with open("student.txt", "r") as f, open("output.txt", "w") as out:
    for line in f:
        data = line.strip().split(",")   # split into list
        
        name = data[0]
        marks = int(data[1])
        sign = data[2]
        
        if marks >= 75:
            out.write(line)

